BPI Systems Inc said it isholding discussions that could lead to the sale of all itsoutstanding shares for about 12 mln dlrs.    BPI president and chief executive officer David R. Fernalddeclined to identify the other party involved in the talks.    For the nine months ended December 31, BPI lost 1,286,000dlrs on sales of 6,452,000 dlrs. Reuter&#3;